messages.content:
Here is a refined answer based only on the provided context:

1. If you have previously imported your LDAP SSL certificates, allow the upgrade to overwrite the certificates.

2. Save or export any custom firewall settings.
   Reapply the firewall settings post Operating System Upgrade.

3. Take a backup on all the vApp VMs.

4. Import the certificates again using the new method described in the Communication security settings section of the Dell M&R Security Configuration Guide, which is available from the Dell Support Site.

5. Save the Java certificates file.
